reviewText: Got this for my mom she likes this guy.... there are a lot of skit things mixed in would have preferred it be straight up stand up comedy. Not horrible but not what we expected.

David is one of the best ventriloquist I have seen and very funny.  I couldn't stop laughing...  Not sure the too short review as this has the TV show episode as well as the full program which is excellent and over an hour long.  I highly recommend this video.
This is quite funny but WAY too short.  Wouldn't buy another one for this price.
